      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROMA KEEPING (2) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 2.75 lengths back in third (35.02) at this track in a Restricted WIN over 600m. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Makes plenty of appeal. JAZZY MCGRAW (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (25.96) last time in a Grade 5 at Q Lakeside. Has ability and is one of the better chances. PROWL (8) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a nose (30.21) behind Georgia Skies at this track. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Expected to be in this for a long way. ARTHUR TANGO (1) surprised many when in the placings last start - deserves some thought.",
